    "created_at": "2017-03-31T14:59:18Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-03-31T14:59:56Z",
    "body": "Right, the distinction I was thinking of was that while `importCertificate` does exactly what the name says it does, `showCertificateTrust` presents a UI where the user can choose what to do. So it's that distinction of do-the-thing vs. ask-the-user-and-maybe-do-it that I was talking about.\r\n\r\nBut like I said, I'm happy to defer to you all on this."
